{"tid":425113,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先返屋企忍唔住攬住老婆喊","createTime":"2017-10-05T12:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T12:44:48.000Z","uid":45173,"like":48,"dislike":226,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"ca278baf2aaf8a829195aff015a316a962985be5","tid":425113,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:07:43.000Z","msg":"今日去Yoho廁所柯屎<br />\n明明做好準備，舖左4層廁紙，再係中間舖一條，墊住我條jer仔<br />\n柯完之後另轉身拎廁紙<br />\n點知觸動左結界<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一波強烈的水花飛濺出來，噴射在我的龜頭附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻起身抹乾淨，但條jer已經濕曬，係全部濕曬。<br />\n出到去餐廳會合老婆，叫佢拎張濕紙巾比我就衝返入廁所抹jer<br />\n成餐飯係度google睇下有無機會患病，完全無講嘢<br />\n頭先返到屋企 老婆問我係咪瀨屎先要濕紙巾<br />\n即刻忍唔住攬住我老婆，大大聲喊左出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb66e9a00d2a57d92bc33d466368fcca8fd6b99","tid":425113,"uid":32699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac257d8b4ee44b982f719faf73861b62018a4d2","tid":425113,"uid":37941,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"好準備身後事"},{"pid":"fdd7fd84e9b8117050a7ff98e51919c93e60a643","tid":425113,"uid":26976,"like":158,"dislike":1,"score":157,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"仲以為你比肥婆污辱咗"},{"pid":"3ab1a8913d5bac68d37e0b5444642fac94c48b22","tid":425113,"uid":2445,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fatcmoji/fat009.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  難得唔怪肥婆事"},{"pid":"043ccc549863b92cf0f80f39384c6af15f8c5f23","tid":425113,"uid":143774,"like":7,"dislike":0